sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Proxy as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant REST as MLServer REST<br/>8080/TCP HTTP (FastAPI)
    participant GRPC as MLServer gRPC<br/>8081/TCP gRPC
    participant DP as DataPlaneHandlers
    participant Batch as Adaptive Batcher
    participant Cache as Response Cache
    participant Registry as MultiModelRegistry
    participant Runtime as Model Runtime<br/>(sklearn/xgboost/lightgbm/onnx)
    participant Storage as /mnt/models<br/>(PVC/Storage Initializer)
    participant Metrics as Metrics Server<br/>8082/TCP HTTP
    participant Prom as Prometheus
    participant Kafka as Apache Kafka<br/>9092/TCP
    participant OTel as OTel Collector<br/>4317/TCP gRPC

    Note over Client,OTel: Flow 1: REST Inference Request

    Client->>Proxy: POST /v2/models/{name}/infer<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    Proxy->>Proxy: Validate token (AuthZ)
    Proxy->>REST: Forward request<br/>HTTP 8080 (pod-internal, plaintext)
    REST->>DP: Route to DataPlaneHandlers.infer()
    DP->>Cache: Check cache (request hash)
    alt Cache Hit
        Cache-->>DP: Cached response
    else Cache Miss
        DP->>Batch: Submit to adaptive batcher
        Batch->>Registry: Dispatch batched request
        Registry->>Runtime: predict(payload)
        Runtime-->>Registry: InferenceResponse
        Registry-->>Batch: Batched result
        Batch-->>DP: Unbatched response
        DP->>Cache: Store in cache
    end
    DP-->>REST: InferenceResponse
    REST-->>Proxy: JSON Response
    Proxy-->>Client: HTTPS Response

    Note over Client,OTel: Flow 2: gRPC Inference Request

    Client->>Proxy: ModelInfer RPC<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    Proxy->>GRPC: Forward<br/>gRPC 8081 (pod-internal, plaintext)
    GRPC->>DP: Route to DataPlaneHandlers.infer()
    DP->>Registry: Dispatch request
    Registry->>Runtime: predict(payload)
    Runtime-->>Registry: InferenceResponse
    Registry-->>DP: Response
    DP-->>GRPC: ModelInferResponse (protobuf)
    GRPC-->>Proxy: gRPC Response
    Proxy-->>Client: HTTPS Response

    Note over Client,OTel: Flow 3: Kafka Streaming Inference (Optional)

    Kafka->>REST: Consume from input topic<br/>KafkaConsumer 9092/TCP
    REST->>DP: Route inference request
    DP->>Registry: Dispatch request
    Registry->>Runtime: predict(payload)
    Runtime-->>Registry: InferenceResponse
    Registry-->>DP: Response
    DP->>Kafka: Publish to output topic<br/>KafkaProducer 9092/TCP

    Note over Client,OTel: Flow 4: Model Loading

    Storage->>Registry: Read model-settings.json<br/>Load model artifacts from /mnt/models
    Registry->>Registry: Validate trusted runtime<br/>(/etc/mlserver/trusted-runtimes.json)
    Registry->>Runtime: runtime.load()
    Runtime-->>Registry: Model ready

    Note over Client,OTel: Flow 5: Metrics & Tracing

    Prom->>Metrics: GET /metrics<br/>HTTP 8082
    Metrics-->>Prom: Prometheus metrics<br/>(request counts, latencies)
    REST->>OTel: Export trace spans<br/>gRPC 4317 (insecure)
    GRPC->>OTel: Export trace spans<br/>gRPC 4317 (insecure)
